Package edu.rosehulman.soar.datamap.actions

Provides action wrappers for various DataMap functions, usually for use within menus.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AddItem Action to add a new DMItem of the specified type to the datamap
ChangeType Action to change an item in the datamap to a different type.
DeleteItem Action to removes an item from the DataMap.
EditComment Action to edit the comment associated with this datamap item.
EditValues Action to call up the editValuesDialog on the given DMItem.
ImportFromVS This is the menu item allowing the datamap to import from the Visual Soar datamap format.
RemoveComment Action to remove the comment from this DMItem.
RenameItem Action to rename an item in the datamap.
SearchFor Action to preform a search on the datamap.
